Greek Taxi Drivers Stage 24-hour Strike, Ta Nea Reports

-- B y   E l e n i   C h r e p a
-- 
2011-07-06T07:24:17Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-06/greek-taxi-drivers-stage-24-hour-strike-ta-nea-reports.html
Greece ’s taxi drivers plan a 24-hour
strike today to oppose the government’s changes in the way
licenses are awarded, T a Nea  reported.  Taxi drivers’ representatives are due to meet with
Infrastructure and Transport Minister Yiannis Ragousis this
morning and plan to drive their vehicles to the ministry, the
newspaper said, without citing anyone.  -- Editor:  Chris Peterson   To contact the reporter on this story:
Eleni Chrepa in Athens at 
